@startuml

[*] --> WaitingForNewSale
state Choice1 <<choice>>
WaitingForNewSale : entry / Start state
WaitingForNewSale : do / Await new sale
WaitingForNewSale : exit / Items selection

WaitingForNewSale --> ItemsSelection : customer arrives

ItemsSelection : entry / Waiting for new sale
ItemsSelection : do / Enter items one by one
ItemsSelection : exit / Payment

ItemsSelection --> Payment : all items added

Payment : entry / Items selection
Payment : do / Choose payment method (cash, card, check)
Payment : exit / Decision making

Payment --> Choice1

Payment : entry / Payment decision
Payment : do / Cash payment
Payment : exit / Sale completion

Payment --> ImmediateSaleCompletion : cash payment

Payment --> Choice2

Payment : entry / Payment decision
Payment : do / Card or check payment
Payment : exit / Payment verification

Choice2 --> VerifyingPayment : card or check

VerifyingPayment : entry / Payment decision
VerifyingPayment : do / Verify payment
VerifyingPayment : exit / Decision making

VerifyingPayment --> Choice1 : approved payment
ImmediateSaleCompletion --> Choice1

Choice1 --> SaleCompletion : sale completed

SaleCompletion : entry / Sale completion
SaleCompletion : do / Complete the sale
SaleCompletion : exit / Return to waiting for new customer

SaleCompletion --> ReturnToWaitingForNewCustomer

ReturnToWaitingForNewCustomer : entry / Sale completion
ReturnToWaitingForNewCustomer : do / Return to waiting for new customer
ReturnToWaitingForNewCustomer : exit / final state

ReturnToWaitingForNewCustomer --> [*]

@enduml
